 “总决赛”增加了游戏模式，这对单人玩家来说是个好消息https://www.nme.com/news/the-finals-adds-game-mode-thats-good-news-for-solo-players-3572293?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-finals-adds-game-模式对于单人玩家来说是个好消息Ryan EasbyWed, 17 Jan 2024 16:51:09 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3572293 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-arena-carriables-damage-players.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="总决赛。图片来源：Embark Studios。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-arena-carriables-damage-players.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-arena-carriables-damage-players-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-arena-carriables-damage-players-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-arena-carriables-damage-players-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-arena-carriables-damage-players-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-arena-carriables-damage-players-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>目前尚不清楚该模式将持续多久</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/the-finals-adds-game-mode-thats-good-news-for-solo-players-3572293">“The Finals”增加了游戏模式，这对单人玩家来说是个好消息，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-arena-carriables-damage-players.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="总决赛。图片来源：Embark Studios。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-arena-carriables-damage-players.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-arena-carriables-damage-players-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-arena-carriables-damage-players-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-arena-carriables-damage-players-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-arena-carriables-damage-players-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-arena-carriables-damage-players-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-finals">总决赛</a></em>今天（1 月 17 日）迎来了大规模的新更新，增加了新的游戏模式、新的服装等等。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/the-last-of-us-part-2-remastered-review-3571657">《最后生还者第二部重制版》评论：令人沮丧，但值得</a></strong></li></ul><p>更新 1.5.0 的主要吸引力是名为“Solo Bank It”的新玩家对玩家模式，它将现有的“Bank It”模式从基于三人组的游戏更改为 12 名玩家互相对抗的游戏模式其他人则试图尽可能多地获取金钱。</p><p>该模式是一个限时活动，除了根据<a href="https://www.reachthefinals.com/patch-notes-7" target="_blank" rel="noopener">补丁说明</a>推出该模式是为了“更多地了解您的体验”之外，没有任何实际迹象表明它会持续多久。开发者<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/embark-studios">Embark Studios</a>将开放一个 Discord 频道来收集有关该模式的任何反馈，并决定需要进行的任何调整。</p><p>此次更新还带来了一些平衡性的变化、游戏玩法的调整，以及对自游戏最初发布以来粉丝们一直抱怨的问题的错误修复。 1.5.0 更新还引入了新的“公平竞赛准则”，该准则被描述为针对游戏中作弊者的新改进检测方法。 </p><figure id="attachment_3570035" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3570035" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3570035" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-best-weapons-tier-list.jpg" alt="总决赛。图片来源：Embark Studios。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-best-weapons-tier-list.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-best-weapons-tier-list-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-best-weapons-tier-list-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-best-weapons-tier-list-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-best-weapons-tier-list-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-finals-best-weapons-tier-list-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3570035" class="wp-caption-text">总决赛。图片来源：Embark Studios。</figcaption></figure><p> “从现在开始，我们将更有信心限制作弊者，并将坚定地支持我们的禁令。我们的目标一如既往，是让游戏安全、公平、有趣。”博客文章中写道。</p><p>在平衡性变化方面，亮点包括多个物品接收新的激活成本和更长的冷却时间，以防止某些动作（例如隐形装置和侦察感知）的垃圾邮件，以及减少游戏模式中某些事件发生所需的时间。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，新的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox</a>系统更新修复了<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xbox-update-fixes-save-destroying-baldurs-gate-3-bug-3572400">《博德之门 3》</a></em>中的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xbox-update-fixes-save-destroying-baldurs-gate-3-bug-3572400">保存破坏错误</a>。</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/the-finals-adds-game-mode-thats-good-news-for-solo-players-3572293">“The Finals”增加了游戏模式，这对单人玩家来说是个好消息，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
